uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.swing

Class SwingFormResultVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.swing.SwingFormResultVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contexed, FormResultVisitor

    public class SwingFormResultVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements FormResultVisitor, Contexed
    a FormResultVisitor that uses Swing windows. To avoid deep recursion this class performs a single transition iteration any subsequent FormResults may be retrieved using getNextResult.

    spb
